g'(c)=0
g'(c) \leq |f'(c)|
g'(c) = \lim_{x\to c} \frac{|f'(x)|-|f'(c)|}{x-c} \leq \left|\lim_{x\to c} \frac{f'(x)-f'(c)}{x-c}\right| = |f'(c)|
g'(c)= \lim_{x \to c} \frac { |f(x)|}{x-c} 
